        "\n",
        "Nitrogen Summary\n",
        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        "## What's Next?\n",
        "\n",
        "🧪 Now let's practice testing nitrate and nitrite content in water samples. We'll complete a brief water quality lab on the next page."
